{
  "chapter": "098",
  "title": "傅靳蒯成列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "傅宽从军功绩",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">阳陵侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">傅宽</span>，以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">五大夫</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑将</span>的身份跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>起兵，起初做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">横阳</span>。 跟从<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻打</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杠里</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">开封</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵贲</span>军，以及<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杨熊</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲遇</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳武</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span>十二级，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卿</span>。 跟随到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">被立为</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅宽\">宽（傅宽）</span>封号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共德君</span>。 跟随入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>，升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右骑将</span>。 跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赐食邑</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雕阴</span>。 跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，待命于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">怀</span>地，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">通德侯</span>。 跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项冠</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周兰</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>，所率士卒<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑将</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖</span>下，增加<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "属淮阴击齐",
      "text": "归属<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴（韩信）</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历下</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田解</span>。归属<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">残破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">博</span>邑，增加<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span>。因而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>世代不绝，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">阳陵侯</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千六百户</span>，除去先前的<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span>。任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐右丞相</span>，防备<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。五年后任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "击陈豨迁代相",
      "text": "四月，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>，归属<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>身份代替<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樊哙\">哙（樊哙）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>。一个月后，调任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，率兵屯守。二年后，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代丞相</span>，率兵屯守。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "傅氏侯位传承",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景侯</span>。 子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">顷侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅精\">精（傅精）</span>继承，二十四年去世。 子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅则\">则（傅则）</span>继承，十二年去世。 子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅偃\">偃（傅偃）</span>继承，三十一年时，因与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">谋反</span>获罪，死，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "靳歙从沛起",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">信武侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">靳歙</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中涓</span>身份跟从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>起兵，起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛朐</span>。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阳</span>。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李由</span>军。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>南、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">开封</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东北</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑千人将</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，首五十七级，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">捕虏</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十三人</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span>封号为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">临平君</span>。 又<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓝田</span>北，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车司马</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑长</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，首二十八级，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">捕虏</span>五十七人。 到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">被立为</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：靳歙\">歙（靳歙）</span>爵为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建武侯</span>，升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑都尉</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "攻陇西平雍丘",
      "text": "跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>。 另率一军向西<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章平</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>之，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span>六县，所率士卒<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车司马</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">候</span>各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑长</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十二人</span>。 跟随东<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战败</span>回师，保<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍丘</span>，前去<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span>反叛者<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王武</span>等。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻略</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地，另率一军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邢说</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">菑</span>南，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>之，亲身<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">擒获</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邢说\">说（邢说）</span>的都尉<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">候</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十二人</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span>吏卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四千一百八十人</span>。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>东。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赐食邑</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四千二百户</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "渡河内平赵楚",
      "text": "另率军到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贲郝</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朝歌</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>之，所率士卒<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">擒获</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑将</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百五十匹</span>。 跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻打</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安阳</span>以东，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘蒲</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻下</span>七县。 另率军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">擒获</span>其将领中<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">候</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span>吏卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千四百人</span>。 跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。 另率军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>，亲身<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守相</span>，所率士卒<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">兵守</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郡守</span>各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄴</span>。 跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朝歌</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，以及另率军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>军，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>郡六县。 回军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>南，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">截断</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军粮道，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襄邑</span>。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项冠</span>军于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>城下。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻略</span>土地，东至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">缯</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郯</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邳</span>，南至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">竹邑</span>。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项悍</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阳</span>下。 又回师<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>下，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span>之。 另率军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江陵</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江陵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柱国</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span>以下<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八人</span>，亲身<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">擒获</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">江陵王</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">活捉</span>押送至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>，因而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南郡</span>。 跟从到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">擒取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>世代不绝，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">定</span>食<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四千六百户</span>，封号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">信武侯</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "击韩王信攻陈豨",
      "text": "以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑都尉</span>身份跟随<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻打</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>下，回军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东垣</span>。 有功，升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车骑将军</span>，并率<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车骑</span>，另率一军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯敞\">敞（侯敞）</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span>之，因而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲逆</span>。 跟从<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>有功，加封<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">定</span>食<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千三百户</span>。 总计<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span>九十级，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">俘虏</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百三十二人</span>；另率军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span>敌军十四次，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span>城池五十九座，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span>郡、国各一，县二十三；<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">擒获</span>王、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柱国</span>各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二千石</span>以下至<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五百石</span>的官员三十九人。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "靳氏侯位传承",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：靳歙\">歙（靳歙）</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">肃侯</span>。子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：靳亭\">亭（靳亭）</span>继承侯位。二十一年时，因役使国人超过法律规定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span>后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，剥夺侯位，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "周緤事迹",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">蒯成侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周緤\">緤（周緤）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>人，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">周氏</span>。 经常做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">参乘</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>身份跟从起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>。 到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>，西入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，回师<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">池阳</span>。 东<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">截断</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甬道</span>，跟随出击渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阴</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襄国</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span>兵会合，战局时顺时不顺，但他始终不离开皇上。 以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周緤\">緤（周緤）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">信武侯</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千三百户</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周緤\">緤（周緤）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">蒯成侯</span>，除去先前的<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "阻高祖亲征",
      "text": "皇上想亲自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">蒯成侯</span>哭着说：\"当初<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">天下</span>，不曾亲自出行。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今上</span>却常亲自出行，这是没有人可派遣了吗？\" 皇上认为他\"爱戴我\"，赐予他入殿门不用快步前行的特权，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>人不处死。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "周氏侯位传承",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周緤\">緤（周緤）</span>以高寿终，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贞侯</span>。子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周昌\">昌（周昌）</span>继承侯位，有罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周緤\">緤（周緤）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周居\">居（周居）</span>继承侯位。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周居\">居（周居）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>，有罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">阳陵侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">傅宽</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">信武侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">靳歙</span>都是高爵位者，跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>名将，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span>敌军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">收降</span>城池以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十计</span>，未曾困窘受辱，这也是天授的。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">蒯成侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周緤</span>秉性坚定正直，自身未受疑忌，皇上想有所行动，未尝不流泪劝谏，这是有伤感之心者的表现，可以说是笃实敦厚的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>了。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅宽\">阳陵（傅宽）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信武</span>，成年时便跟随<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军。 行动契合人谋，功业实为天助。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项籍\">项（项籍）</span>，我军常居首功。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒯成侯周緤\">蒯成（蒯成侯周緤）</span>委身效忠，平险之中不乱。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">主上</span>称赞其忠，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>堪称表率。"
    }
  }
}